import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.lineplot(x='Date', y='CO2', data=data)
    ax.set(xlabel='Date', ylabel='CO2')
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the trend of CO2 concentration over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.ticker as ticker
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.histplot(data=data, x='CO2', kde=True)
    ax.set_xlabel('CO2 Concentration (ppm)')
    ax.set_ylabel('Frequency')
    ax.xaxis.label.set_rotation(0)
    if len(plt.xticks()[0]) > 20:
        ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))
    plt.title('What is the distribution of CO2 concentration?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(6, 6))
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='ignore')
    ax = sns.scatterplot(x='Year', y='CO2', data=data)
    ax.set_title('What is the relationship between CO2 concentration and year?', wrap=True)
    ax.set_xlabel('Year')
    ax.set_ylabel('CO2 concentration (ppm)')
    ax.xaxis.set_major_locator(ticker.MaxNLocator(20))

        tick.set_rotation(90)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
